<paragraph blockId="21.[151,1437,151,719]" box="[199,921,694,719]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,446,694,719]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
Distribution in 
<collectingCountry box="[382,446,694,719]" name="Chile" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Chile</collectingCountry>
</emphasis>
. Only known from Corral (present study).
</paragraph>
